              "settings": {
                "text": "<h2>.125\" thick</h2><p>UHMW (ultra high molecular weight polyethylene) plastic stencils are built for the toughest environments, offering exceptional durability and resistance to wear. This material stands up to abrasion, moisture, and chemicals while maintaining its shape and precision through repeated use.</p><p>When conditions are harsh, UHMW is the material that keeps performing.</p><ul><li>Superior strength and toughness</li><li>Excellent resistance to wear and chemicals</li><li>Low moisture absorption for consistent performance</li></ul>",
